channel.description:

item.title: How do you login to your free website zeeblo.com?
item.dc:creator: @Kryptizzler Kryptizzler
item.description:
@Kryptizzler wrote:

I hate having to post on forums to get hosting. AwardSpace is good hosting.

Edit: I checked and they both have roughly the same stuff. 200mb space, 5gb bandwidth, 1 mysql db etc.

Edit: I had a deeper look and Zeeblo looks pretty cool. There’s higher things and they’re all free too.
